al/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好八字投胎去印度窮鄉，都冇機會發圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以「命」同「運」係分開，八字只可算到「運」高低嘅軌跡<br />\n<br />\n「命」就要睇投胎嗰刻嘅天時（太平 / 戰亂時代）、地利（家底、屋企風水）、人和（身邊六親有冇貴人、小人）、仲有個人選擇（揀放棄人生定積極向上）<br />\n<br />\n如果一個八字可以算晒你六親、兄弟姊妹、另一半、合作夥伴、老闆同事，咁就其他人嘅八字咪 = 廢？"},{"pid":"00d97b5a29c0ee4794bfde692cba969625ef0be5","tid":2373620,"uid":283741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:49:13.000Z","msg":"因為中國佬嘢呃鳩人"},{"pid":"6ba7c6b47f84ad4a1d8b96d648b003a07deaa419","tid":2373620,"uid":242921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"00d97b5a29c0ee4794bfde692cba969625ef0be5","tid":2373620,"uid":283741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:49:13.000Z","msg":"因為中國佬嘢呃鳩人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:53:07.000Z","msg":"正確，算命根本就是自圓其說的騙術大全。"},{"pid":"0bdefbf11e830a149d317479e2c2a1b8caa9cb59","tid":2373620,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:16:07.000Z","msg":"真實命例？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07caace1d087b596e51e8b5f5bd0098301f1184c","tid":2373620,"uid":20979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"八字同，名唔同都可以差好遠啦"},{"pid":"8133944ec21146c71cff6e7d3aabf82207772122","tid":2373620,"uid":223082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"以我既經驗仲好多因素可以左右一個人<br />\n就算係同一個八字性別唔同已經可以好大分別"},{"pid":"aaad9a0b64344148660611f9cdc7cccbc1470178","tid":2373620,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07caace1d087b596e51e8b5f5bd0098301f1184c","tid":2373620,"uid":20979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"八字同，名唔同都可以差好遠啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:28:52.000Z","msg":"啱聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg